re-existing knowledge of the trans community disproves the whole grooming moral panic. I thought I was the only person like this for years until learning about other trans people.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Since I was young in a pre-internet era, I had to learn about trans folk from daytime TV talk shows.  (They were a lot better and less degrading to guests in the pre-Springer era.).  And I had known that I was a girl and knew no one would listen, but the first time I had seen a trans woman on a one of those shows, all I could think is, “She’s like me!” </p>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"elierlick","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":3000,"header_full_height":1055,"avatar_shape":"square","background_color":"#F6F6F6","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/ceb0aa9501fb5df65b643121e98aa573/e25990b1c8737908-39/s3000x1055/b4cabf749504283d7da25069ca88d0b4c074b2a5.png","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/ceb0aa9501fb5df65b643121e98aa573/e25990b1c8737908-39/s2048x3072/4561fb2ab57595d802bb8a4ff7ff98cdf7945f23.png","header_image_poster":"","header_image_scaled":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/ceb0aa9501fb5df65b643121e98aa573/e25990b1c8737908-39/s2048x3072/4561fb2ab57595d802bb8a4ff7ff98cdf7945f23.png","header_stretch":true,"link_color":"#81B4D2","show_avatar":true,"show_description":true,"show_header_image":true,"show_title":true,"title_color":"#444444","title_font":"Helvetica Neue","title_font_weight":"bold"},"share_likes":false,"share_following":false,"can_be_followed":true},"post":{"id":"805857118686248960"},"content_raw":"<p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1746\" data-orig-width=\"1210\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/0c5f02073e3d10709386c5e3abb846db/a6272c5e636c7c1f-f8/s640x960/5e350df312c59c36c956238b8ca583be759c2df1.png\" data-orig-height=\"1746\" data-orig-width=\"1210\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/0c5f02073e3d10709386c5e3abb846db/a6272c5e636c7c1f-f